{"tid":795941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"河南中學逼學生站著吃飯 校方：節約時間放在學習上","createTime":"2018-08-27T11:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T12:01:05.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de9f3ebc330d9a88e48a837822767a4af10f0a39","tid":795941,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180827/_2018082717595882874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180827%2F_2018082717595882874.jpg&h=e752784e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有學生認為校方是為他們著想。梨視頻影片截圖<br />\n<br />\n為了提高學生的就餐效率，以節約更多時間投放在學習上，河南商丘睢縣高級中學把飯堂內的椅子收起，學生由昨日中午起只能站著吃。<br />\n<br />\n商丘睢縣高級中學昨日舉辦開學日，學生中午時分走到飯堂時，發現餐桌竟然不見了，只剩下沒有椅子的餐桌。學生買飯後，就只能站在桌子旁吃飯。<br />\n<br />\n校方今日回應指，此舉是參考了外地的做法，目的是提高學生的吃飯的效率，以節約更多時間投放到學習上。校方又指，下一步要為學生安排指定的進食位置，因為站在指定的位置上吃飯，一般花10分鐘吃飯便可以了。<br />\n<br />\n至於站著吃飯究竟是否健康，湖北襄陽市中心醫院消化內科主任高山指，吃飯要細嚼慢嚥，急速進食對身體不好，一旦吃得快，咀嚼便不充分，會影響消化。他補充，短時間站著吃飯對身體沒有影響，但時間久了可能會引發腸胃的慢性疾病。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/802378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F802378&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=7d4c49b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F802378&h=adf8d9d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/802378</a>"},{"pid":"c5194794b1412f3c5a769f65df6cdae8146bed0f","tid":795941,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:41:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他補充，短時間站著吃飯對身體沒有影響，但時間久了可能會引發腸胃的慢性疾病。</blockquote><br />\n有腸胃病前畢業<br />\n咁就唔關間學校事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc973344d19e3d9deeb5fbdd624bf92a47ecf75","tid":795941,"uid":125479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"畜生先會站立食"},{"pid":"6026d4b5e42d7180f91a13737d51cbe69ee42661","tid":795941,"uid":169662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:49:01.000Z","msg":"企住返工仲好，坐到肚腩都大埋"},{"pid":"a7fb9ff422ebe7b80aacf15e04c0a1b285b0a3cf","tid":795941,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"支取豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc34766fa50b366d28da0ef70dc5000d7c6232f","tid":795941,"uid":87404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:01:05.000Z","msg":"支那 果然有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次可以逼人 倒立食飯 應該會更快食完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}